messageBody:
Well, it was never really dead, just hibernating. The Bible in Quikscript project is back on its feet and now has even more of the New Testament in much, much better formatting than before. If things go at this pace, the New Testament should be ready for final editing soon. Comments are appreciated, and corrections are badly needed.

Check it out at
https://sourceforge.net/projects/web-qs/files/Milestone1/

Thanks!
